title._content: The Tilyou House, Coney Island, November 30, 1874.

description._content: George Bradford Brainerd (American, 1845-1887). The Tilyou House, Coney Island, November 30, 1874. Wet-collodion negative, 3 1/4 x 6 3/4 in. (8.3 x 17.1 cm). Prints, Drawings and Photographs. Brooklyn Museum/Brooklyn Public Library, Brooklyn Collection, 1996.164.2-1136.
